{"tid":808930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[再多一層B4M層]蘋果再揭西九站暗藏「列車人員訪談室」 運房局深夜玩自爆","createTime":"2018-09-06T17:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T05:18:16.000Z","uid":47352,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6df19e28c9a398da8700f8c8b2198eebdc0c576f","tid":808930,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"高鐵西九龍站通車在即，惟公眾至日前才知悉該站暗藏逾3萬呎的B5層空間。《蘋果》翻查圖則再發現 ，原來B4層與B3層之間，亦有一層B4M層（Basement 4M），面積達4.5萬方呎，過去同樣鮮有被提及。《蘋果》早前就此向港鐵查詢，獲告之周五下午回覆，惟運房局周四深夜突然自我引爆。<br />\n根據《蘋果》取得的2017年3月修訂圖則，B4M層位於B3、B4之間的間隔牆內，呈長條形狀，設一條長約500米的通道貫通。4.5萬方呎的空間內有約18間獨立房間，除了一般機電用途房間外，有多間房的圖則名稱包括「MTR Staff」字眼，相信只供港鐵人員使用，當中包括控制室、會面室、貯物櫃室等等。唯獨男女廁、以及另一間「列車人員訪談室（Train Staff Interview Room）」，圖則名稱上未有列明只供港鐵使用。本報就此向港鐵查詢，但未有向運房局提問。<br />\n惟運房局在昨深夜11時02分再次透過政府新聞處發稿，自爆西九龍站內樓層與樓層之間，設有「後勤用地」，分別位於B1售票大堂之上的「B1M」層（5,600平方米）、位於B2入境層之上的「B2H」層（10,300平方米）、位於B3出境層之上的「B3M／B3H」層（7,200平方米）和位於B4月台層之上的「B4M」層（4,200平方米），合共29.4萬呎。局方解釋，有關後勤用地專供放置站內設施，和供廣深港高鐵香港段營運商人員辦公之用，由港鐵公司負責管理，強調這些後勤用地均不屬「內地口岸區」範圍。<br />\n運房局稱，有關用地設有抽風管道、鐵路營運商辦公室、冷氣系統機房設施和垃圾收集用房等，強調有關用地的出入口，均有保安設施上鎖，並會嚴格控制及派員巡邏，禁止未獲授權人士進入。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180907/58653827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58653827&d=GWPW7JtnNR0n12GJohEXkdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6d6c7a5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58653827&h=d9719f8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180907/58653827</a>"},{"pid":"e6f5eec8dc06cd1ccafa4bd7617964f4bfb82784","tid":808930,"uid":84751,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"香港冇架啦<br />\n撞鐵咁搞法大肚婆落黎生仔唔到香港唔車佢入醫院<br />\n仲整19幾部Lift穿梭各個樓層, 俾大陸人偷渡入香港"},{"pid":"535af842d1d7ba3caf8e46da88982c5cd61062b4","tid":808930,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:59:47.000Z","msg":"咁撚多飛地<br />\n<br />\n由B1搭lift去B5,要搞幾多次出入境手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb1ec5628d461823ba9985ffff3050b992ff303","tid":808930,"uid":1372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:12:37.000Z","msg":"訪談，即係拉咗你就係呢啲房度嚴刑逼供<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c33272f8616373f42ed0854903e5335b64c6e4d","tid":808930,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"起埋去B18吖笨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7357afa9178393b43042b8426a6ce947db62b5","tid":808930,"uid":2949,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:16:37.000Z","msg":"訪談室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪開到個冷氣凍一凍 再搵盞大光燈射住你果種"},{"pid":"8461ac66d89145ff9345173969390dacbdc45024","tid":808930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fb1ec5628d461823ba9985ffff3050b992ff303","tid":808930,"uid":1372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:12:37.000Z","msg":"訪談，即係拉咗你就係呢啲房度嚴刑逼供<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T20:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2021e99553827c508282ee6cca49959c69c9bcd4","tid":808930,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T21:18:03.000Z","msg":"hair wash room"},{"pid":"0c93f3de20501b26626210db9164adb564ee1c93